<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LONG CHA FU</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 用豆腐做奶茶，还能当招牌？=</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/014bcfd02fe34d56832eb9fdf1a5638e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/e19a0023c64149608a9ed77ac8b387a8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200923/b450ebf96e5d466eb4c7c90396448a01.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/5cf362cbacde44a384ce4c20275ee04b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">招牌<strong>大宝藏翡翠仙草</strong>，凭借独特的颜值和满满的内料成为店内当红花旦，不试一次你都不知道原来“豆腐”奶茶这么好喝！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 南方才有的翡翠仙草奶茶，一杯5层料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200923/8a0100b7b41948f6aed25dff670bd14d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/c5ddd18b06984bc98865e494b49e1533.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">奶茶要好喝，也需要创新！龙茶傅用<strong>南方独有的翡翠仙草</strong>解锁奶茶新世界~绿色的<strong>仙草为底，铺上芋圆、燕麦、红豆和碎花生</strong>，口感丰富超惊喜~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 仙草or豆腐？嚼着吃的凉茶？！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200923/299a3bf808f24e268f7813f2dbe8b322.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">翡翠仙草不仅吸睛，还大有来头~它又名<strong>观音豆腐、神仙豆腐</strong>，是安徽、浙江一带的特色小吃，<strong>制作工艺已经收录非物质文化遗产</strong>，北方朋友都很少见过~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200923/1e8ea64ec22b42adbd08bfde0d71d482.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">翡翠仙草的前身是<strong>观音树叶</strong>，它不仅能入药，还具有很高的营养价值，清热排毒润肠不在话下，<strong>堪比咱们的广州凉茶</strong>，还不会让你苦到哭！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/1bc0725087e24684a792bf1c7fd87fef.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">观音树叶因为<strong>季节性强且量少</strong>在广州也很少能看到，手工制成翡翠仙草<strong>滑嫩Q弹</strong>，会DuangDuang地跳舞！吃起来<strong>满口清香，清凉感up</strong>，值得一试！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 甄选大别山好茶，手摇出味</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/a467a5ca2e7243ea84e211d3c6845a5d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/b618786e90d247c498289ab369f873af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200923/6e9d391fbced4b67bfc3faca57cd913f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/044aaed4182949d6a38f3721e6c41051.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">一杯好奶茶，茶底也hin重要！大别山腹地，<strong>全国十大生态产茶县金寨县</strong>茶厂直供茶叶，好山好水出好茶！爱喝茶的潮汕人都知道~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/28520538c9264f258aba7fc321dcb7a0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/cb714083aa5349ae8a13e54a3c81603e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">茶底和奶经过店员们的手摇，完美的融合在一起，<strong>奶香茶香清新浓郁</strong>，正不正一口就知道！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>❶代餐低热量，好喝不怕胖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/b5bf356c6add4d9eb0342682641a0b19.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/e158bff7dc6e4b10b19255ce1c6e14b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">大宝藏翡翠仙草<strong>吸睛的撞色，看得见的好料</strong>足以制霸朋友圈~一杯下去，饭钱都省了！翡翠仙草+五谷底料，<strong>热量比一般奶茶低得多</strong>，漂亮宝贝们大胆喝！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/ae1f8ff38f1344509553343f1dda830f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">嘬上一大口，<strong>奶茶的清甜</strong>最先占领味蕾，咀嚼中<strong>碎花生的香气，红豆的软糯，芋圆的Q弹</strong>让人不能自拔，仙草的微苦中和了甜度，<strong>喝不腻还喝不胖</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>LONG CHA FU</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 芝芝梅梅脆啵啵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/6da70d9009e949a095aa99bae63f9093.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">醇厚的奶盖下是满满的草莓果粒冰沙，一口下去<strong>又香甜又有草莓的清香</strong>~杯底的脆啵啵也十分Q弹哟~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/381c8c8b72234086a560f145a24c915d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/029ad56427ed41dd9f967cc183aa6280.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">纯正的草莓红和龙茶傅的复古中国红可太搭了，别忘了来一波美照~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 芒果百香脆啵啵</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/d5e7b9af0d28466ab66934ba80511a8c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">喜欢更清新口味的小伙伴可以选择<strong>芒果百香脆啵啵</strong>，百香果的微酸中和了芒果的丝丝甜味，果香十足~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200923/a1364f92ce784c99a21936e4bd827932.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/eb5386f23cc444ddac9152511cbd7d18.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">龙茶傅的鲜果都是<strong>每日到店，现切现做</strong>，杯杯都能看到<strong>满满果肉</strong>，鲜度拉满！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 紫葡萄碎碎冰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200923/50b800e4b75c4bce8b8c89b3d5afcd9c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/8bdb221a47b347198bb05d7a01c33624.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/5f5a305aa04046049fe09d4d8d024d8c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/b5f53af0c9ed4be2af61dd175bc204b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">葡萄爱好者不能错过的<strong>紫葡萄碎碎冰</strong>！顶级茉莉毛尖茶底搭配大颗紫葡萄果肉，喝到爽~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 西柚益菌多多</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200923/60535e39baf945a0a302fc3c1aac78f1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200923/858583ff0a8e4e8a82306f18e71c330b.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200923/1ae1d881b6034eeaa452f4d058eb39c7.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/0fcbb36454344d97bfc1b135b808548a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">同样满满果肉的<strong>西柚益菌多多</strong>增添了益菌多，粉嫩嫩的颜色也太少女啦~果肉是<strong>真实能嚼到</strong>的哦~~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>● 鸭屎香柠檬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/2bbec4ad2fa84d0d85ca131e652f0616.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/2bbec4ad2fa84d0d85ca131e652f0616.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200923/9d6a13e935284ccd929244d47151bfa3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">回头率超高的<strong>鸭屎香柠檬茶</strong>也hin值得一试！大名鼎鼎的鸭屎香茶叶和柠檬简直就是绝配CP，<strong>清爽解腻</strong>必点，一杯下去整个人从里到外都舒爽~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>04</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>MINI HEYTEA FACTORY</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 新国潮奶茶，喝了今年一定鸿 =</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/e4acb262002e449d892dd3e13756a510.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">●●●</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200923/6c819eb4748b471d8a3dbb16b87740e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200923/aa3942033ecd412b811e9d2717fdce03.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200923/070e0f9c4286434aa8166a8292c76120.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">龙茶傅龙洞店主打红白配色，可以说是<strong>从里红到外</strong>！logo特色鲜明，<strong>国潮味满满</strong>！龙茶傅一共三层，吧台、阁楼、卡座应有尽有，约上朋友聊一整天都没有问题~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/cb194db89cde40389ae4f43d09186497.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
