<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>非 洲 狂 想 曲</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200923/6c7c38fbf72648248a89ca8b5f618c10.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>网红萌物羊驼展</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200923/5f1d44a91ba3483ebf6894c563552c6f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200923/9635815f285a4ae382c959da9d4753ca.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>打卡点：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>动物魔力涂鸦墙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>动物奇趣乐园</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">吸遍猫咪、撸遍狗狗，这次带你来rua羊驼！<strong>与网红萌物近距离接触、喂食...</strong>羊驼们“认真营业”的样子真的超软萌</p>
